  %% Diagram 45A: Order Journey Business-Friendly View

  Start[Buyer places order]
  Confirm[Order confirmed after payment and stock checks]
  Prepare[Vendor prepares package]
  Ship[Delivery partner ships order]
  Receive[Buyer receives order]
  Complete[Order completed]

  Problem{Any problem happens?}
  Fix[Support and protection workflow starts]
  Refund[Refund when claim is valid]
  Resolve[Order continues when issue is resolved]

  Start --> Confirm --> Prepare --> Ship --> Receive --> Problem
  Problem -- No --> Complete
  Problem -- Yes --> Fix
  Fix --> Refund --> Complete
  Fix --> Resolve --> Complete